Actions.Name: Get the dates in history when a series' data values were revised
Actions.Description: Get the dates in history when a series' data values were revised or new data values were released. Vintage dates are the release dates for a series excluding release dates when the data for the series did not change.

Actions.Name: Get a category
Actions.Description: Get a category.

Actions.Name: Get the child categories
Actions.Description: Get the child categories for a specified parent category.

Actions.Name: Get the related categories for a category
Actions.Description: A related category is a one-way relation between 2 categories that is not part of a parent-child category hierarchy. Most categories do not have related categories.

Actions.Name: Get the related tags for tags within a category
Actions.Description: Get the related FRED tags for one or more FRED tags within a category. FRED tags are attributes assigned to series. For this request, related FRED tags are the tags assigned to series that match all tags in the parameters.

Actions.Name: Get all tags
Actions.Description: Get FRED tags. Optionally, filter results by tag name, tag group, or search. FRED tags are attributes assigned to series.

Actions.Name: Get the related tags for one or more tags
Actions.Description: Get the related FRED tags for one or more FRED tags. Optionally, filter results by tag group or search.  FRED tags are attributes assigned to series. Related FRED tags are the tags assigned to series that match all tags in the tag_names parameter and no tags in the exclude_tag_names parameter.

Actions.Name: Get the series matching tags
Actions.Description: Get the series matching all tags in the tag_names parameter and no tags in the exclude_tag_names parameter.
